#Text=Paralympic highlights : September 7 , 2008
#Text=Sunday , September 7 , 2008
#Text=September 7 , 2008 is the 1st major day of the 2008 Paralympic games , the below article summarises all the world records and medals .
#Text=World Records
#Text=Swimming
#Text=In the S13 class , Dzmitry Salei from Belarus set a new world record in the final of the men 's 100m butterfly with his time of 58.89 seconds .
#Text=In the S4 class , Patricia Valle from Mexico set a new world record in Heat 1 of the women 's 100m freestyle event with her time of 2:03.82 minutes .
#Text=In the SM7 class , American swimmer Rudy Garcia Tolson set a new world record in heat two of the men 's 200m individual medley with his time of 2:37.80 minutes .
#Text=In the S8 class , Peter Leek from Australia set a new world record in the first heat of the men 's 100m butterfly with his time of 1 minute and 1.01 seconds .
#Text=In the S8 class , Amanda Everlove from the United States set a new world record in the second heat of the women 's 100m butterfly with her time of 1 minute and 11.64 seconds .
#Text=In the S9 class , Tamas Sors from Hungary set a new world record in the first heat of the men 's 100m butterfly with his time of 59.38 seconds .
#Text=With a time of 4:45.43 , Russian Dmitry Kokarev set a new world record in the S2 class of the men 's 200m freestyle .
#Text=With a time of 1:35.21 , Chinese Du Jianping set a new world record in the S3 class of the men 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=With a time of 1:11.05 , Brazilian Daniel Dias set a new world record in the S5 class of the men 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=With a time of 1:16.65 , Spanish Maria Teresa Perales set a new world record in the S5 class of the women 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=With a time of 3:13.05 , American Miranda Uhl set a new world record in the SM6 class of the women 's 200m individual medley .
#Text=With a time of 2:54.61 , American Erin Popovich set a new world record in the SM7 class of the women 's 200m individual medley .
#Text=Cycling
#Text=In the CP3 class , British cyclist Darren Kenny set a new world record in the qualifying stage of the men 's individual pursuit with his time of 3:36.875 minutes .
#Text=With a time of 4:18.961 , Australians Kieran Modra and Tyson Lawrence set a new world in the B&VI 1-3 class of the men 's individual pursuit .
#Text=With a time of 1:14.936 , British Simon Richardson set a new world in the LC 3-4 class of the men 's 1km time trial .
#Text=With a time of 1:21.157 , Britons Ellen Hunter and Aileen McGlynn set a new world in the B&VI 1-3 class of the women 's 1km time trial .
#Text=Shooting
#Text=With a score of 578 , Russian Valeriy Ponomarenko set a new world in the SH1 class of the men 's P1-10m air pistol .
#Text=Gold medals
#Text=Track Cycling
#Text=Christopher Scott of Australia won the gold medal in the CP4 class of the men 's individual pursuit .
#Text=Darren Kenny of Great Britain won the gold medal in the CP3 class of the men 's individual pursuit .
#Text=Kieran Modra and Tyson Lawrence of Australia won the gold medal in the B&VI 1-3 class of the men 's individual pursuit .
#Text=Simon Richardson of Great Britain won the gold medal in the LC 3-4 class of the men 's 1km time trial .
#Text=Aileen McGlynn and Ellen Hunter of Great Britain won the gold medal in the B&VI 1-3 class of the women 's 1km time trial .
#Text=Judo
#Text=Huaping Guo of China won the gold medal in the -48 kg class Judo .
#Text=Shooting
#Text=Valeriy Pomomarenko of Russia won the gold medal in the SH1 class of the men 's P1-10m air pistol .
#Text=Veronika Vadovicova of Slovakia won the gold medal in the SH1 class of the women 's R2-10m air rifle standing .
#Text=Swimming
#Text=Du Jianping of China won the gold medal in the S3 class of the men 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=David Smetanine of France won the gold medal in the S4 class of the men 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=Daniel Dias of Brazil won the gold medal in the S5 class of the men 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=Dmitry Kokarev of Russia won the gold medal in the S2 class of the men 's 200m freestyle .
#Text=Dzmitry Salei of Russia won the gold medal in the S13 class of the men 's 100m butterfly .
#Text=Sascha Kindred of Great Britain won the gold medal in the S13 class of the men 's 200m individual medley .
#Text=Nely Miranda of Mexico won the gold medal in the S4 class of the women 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=Maria Teresa Perales of Spain won the gold medal in the S5 class of the women 's 100m freestyle .
#Text=Valerie Grand Maison of Canada won the gold medal in the S13 class of the women 's 100m butterfly .
#Text=Miranda Uhl of the United States won the gold medal in the SM6 class of the women 's 200m individual medley .
#Text=Erin Popovixh of the United States won the gold medal in the SM7 class of the women 's 200m individual medley .
